Author: slushypandaboobs
Text: I like to personally victimize myself by going on the dark side of tumblr.

Author: quietlyinteresting
Text: Be kind to yourself. Don’t grade yourself against other girls.   Your you and there them. There’s only one you. No one is quite like you and that’s what makes you unique.   Your potential is limitless. So stop worrying and live your joy. Drink in your beauty.
